high_descs: Walk straight, turn right and walk to the counter to your right.
Pick up the dirty plate with the spatula on it on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the sink to your right.
Place the dirty plate with the spatula on it in the sink, clean it and remove it from the sink.
Turn around, walk straight to the fridge, when you reach the ridge, turn right and walk to the shelf to your left.
Place the plate with the spatula on it on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean plate with spatula on it on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn right and walk around the counter, stopping at the yellow vase.
Pick up the used dish behind the yellow vase on the counter.
Make a left and walk towards the sink.
Wash the used dish in the sink, removing it again.
Turn around, walk forwards, hanging a right at the fridge, until you reach the bookshelf.
Put the dish down on the second shelf up on the bookshelf.
anns.task_desc: Wash a dish in the sink to put it on the bookshelf.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward then right again to face the counter.
Pick up a dirty bowl with a knife in it from the counter top.
Turn around to the left and then turn to the right to face the sink.
Place the bowl and knife in the sink and wash them. Turn off the water and take them out.
Turn around completely and walk to the fridge. Make a right and go forward to the brown shelving unit.
Place the plate and knife on the second shelf of the unit.
anns.task_desc: Wash a knife and plate and put them away.
